dev.lyze.gdxUnBox2d

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.lyze.gdxUnBox2d.GameObject

  • public final class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Main game object of the UnBox library. Holds a Box2D body and behaviours.

    • Method Detail

      • setEnabled

        public void setEnabled(boolean enabled)
        Enables or disables this game object. Calls Behaviour.onEnable() or Behaviour.onDisable() for each behaviour on this game object. Additionally, enables or disables the body in the physics world.
        Parameters:
        enabled - If the game object should be enabled or not.
